{"tid":300461,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友下個月係新加坡尼香港, 求景點推介","createTime":"2017-06-28T02:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T05:32:05.000Z","uid":6034,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03250427377e676bfd4b8c2b1653bc883fe96e4c","tid":300461,"uid":6034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:31:12.000Z","msg":"一 pair 男女主要 shopping 同玩<br />\n<br />\nShopping 我只諗到旺角, 銅鑼灣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ( 香港 shopping 真是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n玩 緊係海洋公園，迪士尼，西貢啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩好提議？"},{"pid":"0604fde068f09cf3d6b41a38880929feba81d8a4","tid":300461,"uid":58685,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:31:58.000Z","msg":"學識打字先喇"},{"pid":"206dc1e669c94b5b24f3485695d1d3ea01d27ce4","tid":300461,"uid":6034,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學識打字先喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1002b8411fe70b9beee4daec41f2ebcc0a4dd8","tid":300461,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:34:45.000Z","msg":"樓主你知唔知香港買野其實平過好多地方<br />\n你朋友一心鳩嗚冇錯喎<br />\n<br />\n唔好帶錯人地買B貨當香港野喎你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eecc542614c4886d779538e743c6da22404041a","tid":300461,"uid":6034,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你知唔知香港買野其實平過好多地方<br />\n你朋友一心鳩嗚冇錯喎<br />\n<br />\n唔好帶錯人地買B貨當香港野喎你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry<br />\n其實我意思係話香港 shopping 嘅地方比較少, 我只係諗到尖沙咀，銅鑼灣，旺角<br />\n其餘商場全部一式一樣<br />\n唔係話佢唔應該來香港買嘢 Sorry"},{"pid":"753ac3ad1de85edc2663bcf47708ec68966400df","tid":300461,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主你知唔知香港買野其實平過好多地方<br />\n你朋友一心鳩嗚冇錯喎<br />\n<br />\n唔好帶錯人地買B貨當香港野喎你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry<br />\n其實我意思係話香港 shopping 嘅地方比較少, 我只係諗到尖沙咀，銅鑼灣，旺角<br />\n其餘商場全部一式一樣<br />\n唔係話佢唔應該來香港買嘢 Sorry</blockquote><br />\n呢幾個地方每一個都可消費半日或者一日，你朋友黎十日?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7710cbec34e1bc0b9074e43ba016f6e4170b3f0","tid":300461,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主你知唔知香港買野其實平過好多地方<br />\n你朋友一心鳩嗚冇錯喎<br />\n<br />\n唔好帶錯人地買B貨當香港野喎你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry<br />\n其實我意思係話香港 shopping 嘅地方比較少, 我只係諗到尖沙咀，銅鑼灣，旺角<br />\n其餘商場全部一式一樣<br />\n唔係話佢唔應該來香港買嘢 Sorry</blockquote><br />\n仲有D好野，潮野全集中在呢3個地方唔駛你周圍貢你仲想點😂😂"},{"pid":"08b4305106482ed4737a727ac0fb0fe461ce3c98","tid":300461,"uid":6034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主你知唔知香港買野其實平過好多地方<br />\n你朋友一心鳩嗚冇錯喎<br />\n<br />\n唔好帶錯人地買B貨當香港野喎你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry<br />\n其實我意思係話香港 shopping 嘅地方比較少, 我只係諗到尖沙咀，銅鑼灣，旺角<br />\n其餘商場全部一式一樣<br />\n唔係話佢唔應該來香港買嘢 Sorry</blockquote><br />\n仲有D好野，潮野全集中在呢3個地方唔駛你周圍貢你仲想點😂😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都明嗰3度地方齊晒所有野<br />\n嗰3個地方佢都自己提咗話會去<br />\n弊在佢問我有冇其他地方介紹呢<br />\nSorry 199"},{"pid":"07dffd75a893ff5dab66c872fda08bd7883acc6e","tid":300461,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主你知唔知香港買野其實平過好多地方<br />\n你朋友一心鳩嗚冇錯喎<br />\n<br />\n唔好帶錯人地買B貨當香港野喎你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry<br />\n其實我意思係話香港 shopping 嘅地方比較少, 我只係諗到尖沙咀，銅鑼灣，旺角<br />\n其餘商場全部一式一樣<br />\n唔係話佢唔應該來香港買嘢 Sorry</blockquote><br />\n仲有D好野，潮野全集中在呢3個地方唔駛你周圍貢你仲想點😂😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一陣叫你帶完廸爉尼公園再去西貢食海鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好同人講話坐地鐵巴士去添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8b04338da39f4c8b9c5df6ebd7b23eaee075d6","tid":300461,"uid":73356,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:56:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學識打字先喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尼你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724a1a81753e078bad6dda1106463ac80c5237d6","tid":300461,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都明嗰3度地方齊晒所有野<br />\n嗰3個地方佢都自己提咗話會去<br />\n弊在佢問我有冇其他地方介紹呢<br />\nSorry 199</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你自己有冇諗過先？"},{"pid":"4f4a88c6fe9f6bce7baa92db18ce1ec8c6423c75","tid":300461,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:57:36.000Z","msg":"LKF"},{"pid":"cf1228fbefe28ff6219406886f0f2e0336ea46b4","tid":300461,"uid":23683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:59:07.000Z","msg":"帶佢去海洋公園迪士尼同蝗迫係做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n緊係飲下茶 食茶記 搭叮叮 小巴 遊下車河仲過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babc01da963d90af449a3ee45d72a2141b236be6","tid":300461,"uid":6034,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:59:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學識打字先喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尼你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用左語音輸入，懶得打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71cea9e43fdf5891a9891b9ca3f5be327584745e","tid":300461,"uid":6034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T03:03:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都明嗰3度地方齊晒所有野<br />\n嗰3個地方佢都自己提咗話會去<br />\n弊在佢問我有冇其他地方介紹呢<br />\nSorry 199</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你自己有冇諗過先？</blockquote><br />\n海洋公園，迪士尼，旺角，銅鑼灣，灣仔<br />\n馬場，山頂，赤柱，馬交<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有諗過去博物館，但香港康文署博物館對比起新加坡實在太hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302ffe0ca70755aaeaa768fd6ba827f7c20be05c","tid":300461,"uid":44678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T03:03:35.000Z","msg":"帶佢一齊同你學打字班啦"},{"pid":"dcd9d49b5e21e5864fb321eb7db7eaf9c0dada12","tid":300461,"uid":6034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T03:05:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶佢一齊同你學打字班啦</blockquote><br />\n我識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739eb4415fadd5913dfa1b338a0197c2aed9c550","tid":300461,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T03:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都明嗰3度地方齊晒所有野<br />\n嗰3個地方佢都自己提咗話會去<br />\n弊在佢問我有冇其他地方介紹呢<br />\nSorry 199</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你自己有冇諗過先？</blockquote><br />\n海洋公園，迪士尼，旺角，銅鑼灣，灣仔<br />\n馬場，山頂，赤柱，馬交<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有諗過去博物館，但香港康文署博物館對比起新加坡實在太hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你就返時間、路線咁揀，俾著你去旅行你都會咁啦，避免花過多時間（同錢）喺交通上。<br />\n<br />\n除非你車人地，但例如，如果一定要有廸蠟尼同西貢，我就寧願分兩日去。"},{"pid":"2097b081f8982bf1d7213169cd93fa1ad1cdad79","tid":300461,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:33:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都明嗰3度地方齊晒所有野<br />\n嗰3個地方佢都自己提咗話會去<br />\n弊在佢問我有冇其他地方介紹呢<br />\nSorry 199</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你自己有冇諗過先？</blockquote><br />\n海洋公園，迪士尼，旺角，銅鑼灣，灣仔<br />\n馬場，山頂，赤柱，馬交<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有諗過去博物館，但香港康文署博物館對比起新加坡實在太hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有大把地方，例如九龍城食秦國菜，去圓方撞明星，去大澳/大嶼山食好鮮。去灣仔溝賓妹，去廟街食煲仔飯，去東涌睇大佛同搭䌫車，上山頂睇臘像館，問你夠未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdb47b3ae8bb73359f81ed63081eb93c613cfce","tid":300461,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:08:30.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n嚟香港旅遊唔係搵香港人做導遊嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人根本唔識遊香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢一齊報啲鬼佬團吧啦"},{"pid":"1ef6f0b4483d1efb7b673da6eb02e1731281785e","tid":300461,"uid":5104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:32:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學識打字先喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母仲比膠人，字都唔識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}